Myrmidon trailed the canine formed Trelos for short time, but as Trelos
continued swimming without offereing anything remotely resmbling fun he
lost interest. With a mental shrug moved swiftly to the surface, leaped
out of the water, shifted to his avian form and moved quickly towards
Hydras' base. 

Preston
(Myrmidon)
